{"word":"ὑποξυράω","slug":"ὑποξυράω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑποξυράω</b></el> <el><b>-έω</b></el> <p/><i>to shave</i> or <i>cut off some of the</i> hair: —<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <el>ὑπεξυρημένος</el> <i>shorn</i> or <i>shaven</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/>"}]}